				"post_title": "<i class=\"fa fa-pencil\"><\/i> Login To A Dashboard",
				"post_content": "In this step we begin developing our JavaScript application by laying out our initial files, setting up out index.html file, and start placing elements in our page through manipulating the DOM.\r\n<h3>Action Items to Complete<\/h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n \t<li>Complete all steps completed in the video \u201cinside out \u2013 STEP 401 | Login To A Dashboard\u201d.\r\n<ul id=\"videoLinks\">\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=0s\">00:00 - Introduction <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=33s\">00:33 - project step overview <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=130s\">02:10 - create our index.html page <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=160s\">02:40 - add the viewport meta tag <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=211s\">03:31 - go to cloudflare.com to get animate.css <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=231s\">03:51 - search for animate.css on cloudflare.com <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=236s\">03:56 - copy animate.css link from cloudflare <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=248s\">04:08 - link animate.css in our index.html file <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=282s\">04:42 - create the assets folder <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=291s\">04:51 - create the assets\/js folder <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=294s\">04:54 - create the assets\/js\/app.js file <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=314s\">05:14 - look at how in DW we access linked files <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=342s\">05:42 - link assets\/js\/app.js file to index.html <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=398s\">06:38 - begin coding in assets\/js\/app.js file <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=417s\">06:57 - add 'use strict'; to app.js <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=449s\">07:29 - add the applicationTitle variable <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=489s\">08:09 - add the applicationTagLine variable <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=607s\">10:07 - add the function initializeApplication() <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=646s\">10:46 - add document.title = applicationTitle; <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=717s\">11:57 - add the window.addEventListener <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=822s\">13:42 - add the document.body.styles <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=958s\">15:58 - add the var elWrapper <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=1165s\">19:25 - add the var elHeader <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=1263s\">21:03 - add the var elHeaderTitle <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=1432s\">23:52 - add the var elHeaderTagLine <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=1604s\">26:44 - add elHeaderTagLine.style.fontSize <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=1660s\">27:40 - add the var elMain <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=1732s\">28:52 - add the var elFooter <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=1815s\">30:15 - add the animate css to the elements <\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=yNO7bGcy-mo&amp;t=1955s\">32:35 - clean up code<\/a><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<\/li>\r\n \t<li>Add &amp; commit your work in your repository and then push your work to GitHub.<\/li>\r\n \t<li>Comment a link to your repository in the\u00a0bottom of the body of your index.html page.<\/li>\r\n \t<li>Put all the files you have created to your server and review that your work is error free and aligns to the completed work in the video.<\/li>\r\n \t<li>Submit the url to your application (the index.html file) once you have validated your work and are confident you have completed everything. The link should look similar to the following link:\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/step-401.inside-out-project.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https:\/\/step-401.inside-out-project.com<\/a>\u00a0and\u00a0your page should look to what you see when clicking on the example link.<\/li>\r\n<\/ol>\r\n<ul class=\"lessonResourceLinks\">\r\n \t<li><a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-default\" href=\"http:\/\/step-401.inside-out-project.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><i class=\"fa fa-chrome fa-1x\"><\/i> Step Example<\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-default\" href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/inside-out-project\/step-400\/tree\/step-401\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><i class=\"fa fa-github fa-1x\"><\/i> Step Repository<\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-default\" href=\"https:\/\/dev01.inside-out-project.com\/forums\/forum\/inside-out-project-iop-4xx\/\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><i class=\"fa fa-wpforms fa-1x\"><\/i> inside out project | IOP-4XX Forum<\/a><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<h6>please note: your assignment is to be submitted in the step folder as shown in the example above.<\/h6>\r\n<\/blockquote>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>RACC STUDENTS: Please review the rubric for this assignment and submit this assignment in Canvas.<\/strong><\/span><\/h4>\r\n[pods name=\"knowledge_resource\" where=\"lessons_used_in.ID = 10753\" template=\"Lesson Resources Template\"]",
